import "./barstyle.css"
import Home from "../pages/home.js"
import Secret from "../pages/secret.js"
export default function bar() {
    return(
        <Router>
            <Navbar />
            <Routes>
                <Route exact path="/" element={<Home />} />
                <Route path="/secret" element={<Secret />} />
            </Routes>
        </Router>
    )
}
